  "description": "MUST activate before writing/editing/deleting any class/id/function. 45 commands. v6.1: CMake/C++ project identity (CMakeLists.txt parsing, project name/version extraction, cpp-game-engine/cpp-graphics/qt-desktop-app/cpp-mobile-app classification), Lua entry points (dofile, require, core.register_*/minetest.register_* patterns), C++ entry points (WinMain, wmain, SDL_main, DllMain), GLSL shader language detection, removed C/C++/Java/Kotlin/Lua from unsupported_langs (all have fallback parsers), fixed .h files classified as C instead of C++, game engine directory hints (builtin, mods, games, textures, shaders, etc.), C++/Lua/GLSL tooling recommendations (clang-tidy, cppcheck, luacheck, glslangValidator), fixed architecture total_files counting only tree-sitter-supported languages. Tested on minetest/minetest (2430 files, C++/Lua/GLSL game engine).",  "author": "codelens",
